Salon Reservation System

A simple salon management web application built with Node.js, Express, MongoDB, and Pug.  
It includes an Admin Dashboard where you can manage salon services and reservations.


Features

Admin Panel
- Add, edit, delete salon services  
- Manage customer reservations  
- View all services and bookings in tables  
- Simple confirmation prompt before deletion  

Services Management
- CRUD operations for salon services  
- Each service includes: name, category, price, and description  

Reservation Management
- CRUD operations for reservations  
- Each reservation includes: name, email, date, time and a submit button 
